                                  <ul class="dropdown-menu">\
                                        <li><a href="#" onclick= "showMoreDetails(' + data[i]["DeductionByInstitutionId"] + ')">View</a></li>\
                                  </ul>\
                                </div> </div>'
                                    ]);
                                }
                }
            },
            failure: function (error) {
